  <relatedmaterial id="aspace_a04e30f8671a9bde5fa1c8b17a5cac2c">
    <head>RELATED MATERIALS</head>
<p>The films <extref href="https://media.library.cornell.edu/media/Helen+Powell+Smith/1_8j110ba6/7781881"> <title>Helen Powell Smith</title> </extref> and <extref href="https://media.library.cornell.edu/media/Railroad+Exhibits/1_4cm5pkp8/7781881"> <title>Railway Exhibit - Farm and Home Special</title> </extref> from this collection have been digitized and can be found on Cornell's Library Media Space website along with other Home Economics and related films.</p>  </relatedmaterial>
  <prefercite id="aspace_d28df899d1ffc81cc9d45c8ac737b0fe">
    <head>Cite As:</head>
<p>Elmer S. Phillips papers, #21-42-3218. Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</p>  </prefercite>
  <bioghist audience="internal" id="aspace_32cab07935ef21ce65021cca06c11300">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Elmer Strobel Phillips was a Professor Emeritus, Communication, New York State College of Agriculture and Life Sciences at Cornell University. Phillips was a founding member of a wine appreciation society in Ithaca that later became the American wine society.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_2ad61a1dc21e9f5c2004a4dadf7c3c9e">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Correspondence, lecture notes, publications, photographs, slides, and other papers of a Communications professor.  Includes photographs of the 1937 Ithaca flood, aerial views of Cornell (1937) and movie films taken by Phillips, including Cornell University scenes, faculty members, academic activities, sports, campus events and agricultural activities at Cornell.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_50aa1f8c6ce109a4077d4655b4cac481">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes silent black and white film, silent color film, and sound color film of Cornell University campus scenes, faculty members, academic activities, sports, campus events, and agricultural activities at Cornell.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <scopecontent audience="internal" id="aspace_053de8611b0f24b49ebbcc24c2c091d5">
    <head>Scope and content</head>
<p>Includes copies of the American Wine Society Journal and the Tompkins County Hospital newsletter, Hospital Highlights.</p>  </scopecontent>
